    "The motivation behind RWKV is to balance computational efficiency with expressive capacity in neural networks.",
    "It offers a solution for handling large-scale models with billions of parameters, exhibiting competitive performance at a reduced computational cost.",
    "Experiments suggest RWKV addresses scaling and deployment challenges in AI, especially for sequential data processing, pointing towards more sustainable and efficient AI models.",
    "Our contributions in this paper are as follows:",
    "• The introduction of RWKV, a novel architec-ture combining RNNs and Transformer advantages while mitigating their limitations."
